aboration with a designer’s requirements, adapting one of our designs to their special needs. Hand–woven Italian Silk  hand woven italian silks italian A bouclé called Riccio and a ribbon silk called Fettuccia, woven by hand in our workshop in 16 colors. The yarn is heavy, 2Nm and the result is incredibly sophisticated, transforming a plain silk into a textured fabric resembling macarons or bonbons. Stocked Hand Weaves  stocked handweves stocked We stock a range of hand-woven silks we call Buy Me Now. Interior designers often want cushion fabric at the end of a project and they are happy to have lengths as small as one meter available to them with immediate delivery. Linens & Cottons  linens and cottons cottons Woven in the United Kingdom by our local weaving partners, this range of fabric can be use for window dressing, upholstery or soft furnishings. It is a weave down of our hand woven designs and contains some silk to bring out the color in the figure designs and to soften the texture of the fabric. Mohair velvet  mohair velvets mohair This is a plain piece-dyed fabric with a design etched into the weave, suitable for upholstery. The mohair velvet is woven with the best quality mohair one can find on the market. It is woven in Belgium by experts and available as a stocked fabric item. ','2015-09-10 20:04:40','2'),
